A '''Westphal balance''' (also known as a '''Mohr balance''') is a [[scientific instrument]] for measuring the [[density]] of liquids.<ref>[http://www.mineralogy.eu/non-optical/sg/Mohr-Westphal_01.html Mohr-Westphal balance], Virtual Museum of the History of Mineralogy</ref><ref>[http://physics.kenyon.edu/EarlyApparatus/Fluids/Westphal_Balance/Westphal_Balance.html Westphal Balance], Instruments for Natural Philosophy</ref><ref>[http://www.lecompendium.com/dossier_meca_07_balance_de_westphal/balance_de_westphal.htm Balance de Westphal], Le Compendium</ref>

